polis Colts|Baltimore Colts]], 1950<br />[[Tennessee Titans|Houston Oilers]], 1960\u201366<br />[[Oakland Raiders]], 1967\u201375\n|-\n|[[Dermontti Dawson]]\n|[[Center (American football)|C]]\n|2012\n|[[Pittsburgh Steelers]], 1988\u20132000\n|}\n\n===College===\nSeven Kentucky Wildcat individuals have been inducted into the [[College Football Hall of Fame]].\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Kentucky Wildcats|Inductee|Position|Class|Career}}\n|-\n|[[Art Still]]\n|[[Defensive End|DE]]\n|2015\n|1974\u20131977\n|-\n|[[Bear Bryant|Paul \"Bear\" Bryant]]\n|[[Head Coach]]\n|1986\n|1946\u201353\n|-\n|[[Jerry Claiborne]]\n|[[Head Coach]]\n|1999\n|1982\u201389\n|-\n|[[Bob Gain]]\n|[[Guard (American football)|G]], [[Tackle (American football)|T]]\n|1980\n|1947\u20131950\n|-\n|[[Steve Meilinger]]\n|[[Defensive Line|DL]]\n|2013\n|1951\u201353\n|-\n|[[Lou Michaels]]\n|[[Defensive tackle|DT]]\n|1992\n|1955\u201357\n|-\n|[[Babe Parilli]]\n|[[Quarterback|QB]]\n|1982\n|1949\u201351\n|}\n\n==Future opponents and schedules==\n===Conference and non-conference opponents===\n====SEC West opponents====\nKentucky plays Mississippi State as a permanent non-division opponent annually and rotates around the ''West'' division among the other six schools.<ref name=\"nondivopp\">{{cite web| title=SEC Future Football Schedule Rotation Announced| publisher=fbschedules.com| url=http://www.fbschedules.com/2014/05/sec-future-football-schedule-rotation-2025/| accessdate=June 14, 2014| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605181644/http://www.fbschedules.com/2014/05/sec-future-football-schedule-rotation-2025/| archive-date=June 5, 2014| url-status=live}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Kentucky Wildcats|color=white}}; text-align:center;\"\n| '''Year''' || '''Alabama''' || '''Auburn''' || '''Arkansas''' || '''LSU''' || '''Mississippi State''' || '''Ole Miss''' || '''Texas A&M''' \n|- align=center\n| '''2021''' || ||  || || HOME || AWAY || |